Name: Full Text Search 6.0.2
Description:
This release is compatible with Umbraco *6.0.0* to *6.1.2*.

Most users will simply want the {"Full_Text_Search_6.0.2.zip"} package. 
An additional package that installs a web service to allow scheduled/remote triggering of index updates is provided.
